      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "桌面上撒了一把图钉，我们想知道：这堆点到底有多宽？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "也就是相距最远的那两个点，隔着多远的距离。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "朴素做法是两两比较，点一多就慢得让人着急。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "旋转卡壳给出了一个又快又优雅的答案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "hull",
      "line_id": "hull-1",
      "filename": "hull-hull-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/hull-hull-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "第一步，用一根橡皮筋把所有点箍起来，得到的外轮廓就是凸包。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "hull",
      "line_id": "hull-2",
      "filename": "hull-hull-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/hull-hull-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "最远的两个点一定都在凸包上，内部的点不可能更远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "hull",
      "line_id": "hull-3",
      "filename": "hull-hull-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/hull-hull-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "于是问题从整堆点，缩小到了凸包的少数几个顶点上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "antipodal",
      "line_id": "anti-1",
      "filename": "antipodal-anti-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/antipodal-anti-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "想象用两条平行的直线，从两侧把凸包夹住。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "antipodal",
      "line_id": "anti-2",
      "filename": "antipodal-anti-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/antipodal-anti-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "两条线各自贴着的那对顶点，就叫一组对踵点对。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "antipodal",
      "line_id": "anti-3",
      "filename": "antipodal-anti-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/antipodal-anti-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "凸包的直径，一定出现在某一组对踵点对之间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "rotate",
      "line_id": "rot-1",
      "filename": "rotate-rot-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/rotate-rot-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "让这对平行卡钳贴着凸包慢慢旋转一圈。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "rotate",
      "line_id": "rot-2",
      "filename": "rotate-rot-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/rotate-rot-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "每转到一条边，对面的顶点就随之推进，所有对踵点对被一次扫完。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "rotate",
      "line_id": "rot-3",
      "filename": "rotate-rot-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/rotate-rot-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "同样的旋转还能顺手量出最小面积的外接矩形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "换换点的数量，看凸包和那条粉色直径怎样变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "点击重新随机，每一次都能立刻卡出新的最远点对。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "summary",
